name: Surreality
description:
Please consider visiting my patreon, the first post is a full wildcard of my 1,240 prompts for this model. It's a fast track way to use my model for creativity and see the full potential.

See 1330 txt2img unprocessed samples from this model in an interactive mosaic here
https://mosaically.com/photomosaic/chaingirl-surreality

This is my surreal realism model. Surreality. This is my first release publicly but I've created models amongst friends and small community and directly for clients, but if people like this I will either extend it or create new models on other styles.

It's mostly SFW as it's trained directly on SD1.5 and has no merges.

Prompting

All my examples here are basic prompts. I left my stable diffusion webui generating 1k images with a wildcard of the prompts I trained. No cherry picking to upload, just grabbed any random images from the outputs. Use chaingirldark style when prompting

Sample prompts

  1. a path through a forest with lots of trees and lights on it's sides and a trail leading to the trees , chaingirldark style lightning storm, speedpainting, matte painting, concept art, 4k

  2. two horses running in a field in the foggy day time, with one horse looking at the camera , chaingirldark style ultra detailed, 8k, 35mm lens, beautiful, classical painting, smoke tendrils, clouds, foggy, volumetric lighting, cloudy, trending on Artstation, concept art, hyperdetailed, hyperrealistic

  3. a black and white photo of a church on a rocky hill with a stream running between it and a tree , chaingirldark style digital art, photorealistoc, art by greg rutkowski, hyperdetailed, western comic style, comic, comic style, sharp lineart, professional lighting, deviantart, artstation, trevor henderson, rossdtaws, cinematic, dramatic

  4. a desk with a computer and a monitor on it in a room with a lot of windows and plants , chaingirldark style cyberpunk 2077, blade runner, neon volumetric lights, 35mm lens, beautiful lighting, hyper detailed, digital art, trending in artstation

  5. a city street with a lot of flowers and buildings in the background at night time with pink and purple lights , chaingirldark style cyberpunk, futuristic, ultra detailed, concept art

  6. check example images metadata or my patreon wildcard for more prompts


    Negative prompt: boring, 3d render, long neck, out of frame, extra fingers, mutated hands, , ((poorly drawn hands)), 3DCG, cgstation, extra heads, close up, text ,watermarks, logo

Training:

Finetuned SD1.5 with 1200 surreal and sci-fi images. No merges.

  • trained chaining resolutions from low 300px up to 768px in increments

  • overall 36 epochs 29,970 steps when combining epoch's on lower res training with the 768 training
